{"tid":2064932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人又空投病毒俾美帝","createTime":"2020-06-15T07:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T07:43:09.000Z","uid":111253,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0d038d209112b5e49f1d99b11b90b82e7ac414","tid":2064932,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"陶傑 Channel<br />\n<br />\n據報這是昨天北京飛洛杉磯的航班，都有美國綠卡。<br />\n在班次限制的情況下，飛美國的航機是班班客滿。<br />\n當初武漢疫情爆發，這群人馬上從中國跑到美國。<br />\n後來美國疫情控制不住了，這群人又從美國跑回中國。<br />\n現在北京爆出來疫情，他們又從北京再次跑回美國。<br />\n都是同一群人。你們累不累啊？<br />\n只要美國那邊千萬不要將居留權給「制裁」掉，就不累。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3iyOdo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3iyOdo.jpg&h=2e62a7da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n才子有無炒車?"},{"pid":"4ac77f73bb3159e5838455adba7d53e8b3db5f81","tid":2064932,"uid":67016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:15:36.000Z","msg":"美國咪又係咁嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3dde1bde9187cd79a8a5cf486a48c4ab1b8ff8","tid":2064932,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:23:07.000Z","msg":"美國都識投比支那啫"},{"pid":"2eb37fe54458d8e40455596356e6155c3078a3c6","tid":2064932,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b3dde1bde9187cd79a8a5cf486a48c4ab1b8ff8","tid":2064932,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:23:07.000Z","msg":"美國都識投比支那啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:25:21.000Z","msg":"好地地點解要去地獄鬼國? 係支那人先咁無恥兩邊飛"},{"pid":"bb28b83b7ba4710516d497380595905e71e4cbbe","tid":2064932,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:27:51.000Z","msg":"RACIST<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"